Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还早着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.52,0:00:12.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是雪雪太贪心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.91,0:00:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捡栗子捡个不停才弄得这么晚的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是无可奈何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.59,0:00:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫我家是大家庭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋妈妈太不可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不得不照料大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:28.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕个什么劲儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是只鸟罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.77,0:00:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个羽毛是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:18.96,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想找到 蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天早上都不休息地反复挥刀  真了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是儿时养成的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且呢  不好好练习的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一有一天能离开这个岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个人我是无论如何都想赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腋下太松垮了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  我去河边洗脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能早点回去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是太任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然希望行人无法回去  一直留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是打得稍稍重了点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:50.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好啊雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么早要到哪去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:54.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:03:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在南边和西边的交界处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了看到了 雪乃我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鸟啊  蓝色的鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.81,0:04:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就是证据
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我在南边的森岭捡栗子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家的途中不经意间看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是至今还没被人见到过真面目的那只传说中的蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这个是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多别的拥有蓝色羽毛的鸟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能是绫音故意涂上色做的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为动物博士的我都没看到过的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有这么美丽的羽毛的蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什么样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想见见它并和它成为朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  所以小铃姐你也一起帮我找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不和行人说一下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔兔去把行人带到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:53.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:59.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天还要去捡柴…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管了别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃去找蓝鸟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚幻的蓝鸟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Unidentified Mysterious Animal  未确认动物）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个岛上也有UMA啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.85,0:05:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UMA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未被确认的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还未被发现的新种类的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  对我来说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也称得上是未知的珍兽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是行人你不是对不可靠的事物都持否定的态度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UMA和其他的是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在理论上是可以解释的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  听说如果能抓住蓝鸟就能获得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来叫行人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一会再去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天必须去捡柴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿小铃没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然丢下了捡柴的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪雪硬把她带走的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙捡柴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在行人正一个人捡着柴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  停下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到蓝鸟的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快开始搜索吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有鹰鹰和猫头鹰在就轻松多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是它们昨晚就和妈妈一起去山上泡温泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我回到家的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只留下了「我们去温泉了」的纸条
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢早上睡懒觉  早上喝酒和早上泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是一个废柴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:57.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把女儿丢下不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话就只靠我们几个人找出蓝鸟好好地炫耀一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭借这个气味去找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似只是羽毛进了鼻子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为已经受潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天下了雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说小铃  再到更深处去看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  小铃没有一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想一下的话  自从到了岛上我们大多数时间都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说我给小铃添了这么多的麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都让她这么费心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都没帮上什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧走吧走吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是轻易能找到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是所谓的虚幻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  能找到蓝鸟的话就能带来幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是童话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,童话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小的时候千影姐姐经常读给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  能带来幸福只限于童话中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.67,0:08:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事我当然知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来只限于童话故事中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅是与未知的动物交朋友这点不就足够幸福了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是雪雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是蓝鸟真的能带来幸福的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃姐想要怎样的幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:08:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的话  一直维持现在的样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  只要大家都能健健康康的就算幸福了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闻到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一块的气味很重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吓到它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要悄悄地接近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚幻的蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是没见过的鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是完全都看不出是蓝颜色的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱跑一气的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是会迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小鸟  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有深沟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚才回来对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直找不到合适的柴火…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃姐你快起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:10:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃你早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说早安的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是悠闲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我们掉到深沟里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为雪雪暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能爬得上去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚肿起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是掉下来的时候扭到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很痛的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不碍事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 脚是这种情况要爬上去是不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边缘太松了  不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边缘比我想像的还要脆弱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是行人的话  在这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  已经让兔兔去通知行人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人应该已经察觉到我们出事了才对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来找我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:12:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这里可是森林的最深处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有发现这个洞的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸猪排鼻子很灵敏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人脑袋很好使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  雪乃她们没在小铃家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃也没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道在山里出了什么不测
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道会这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就带他们一起去泡温泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:34.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能冷静的下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果大家出了什么不测
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么不测  这是什么话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全陷入混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情绪变得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去山上找找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜小姐就在村子里找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野猪和猫头鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们去帮助行人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天见到蓝鸟的就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗狗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是小铃她们身边发生了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是在森林中迷路了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了炸猪排  到你出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照气味去寻找小铃她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.15,0:13:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小铃那边也有鼻子很灵的狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅是因为迷路的话不会回不来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是遇到了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天彻底黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带了樱桃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特地摘给行人和炸猪排的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家分着吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊  行人他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟去哪找了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:43.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃姐你还真沉着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我紧张地受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也有被困在洞中的情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候行人很沉着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在想  要是我也能冷静下来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会有办法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃姐真坚强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和小铃姐一起真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你什么都会做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又很可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身材也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:15.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在我这个年纪已经在那个家里独自生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想像小铃姐那么坚强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没有这回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:22.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:27.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的气味会被冲走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最糟的情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸猪排  野猪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气味怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨声太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音似乎也传的不远
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃现在一定是忐忑不安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才好像有谁在叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在叫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想让我跟着你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道小铃她们在哪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能给人带来幸福的蓝鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不相信这种迷信的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.27,0:17:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我小铃在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会跟丢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小铃的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃  雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  我们在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人来救我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  蓝…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  到哪去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幻影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  好难为情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不得安宁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然会掉到那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃也真是笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛  只要没事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了防止再有人掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想做一个栅栏之类的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为这个笨蛋才让你遇到这么大的麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.96,0:18:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是能再小心点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃还真是可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也给我学着点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  还真是个小鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.94,0:19:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像我这样绑根安全绳的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是很危险的 绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也有一个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  一起吃我带来慰问大家的温泉馒头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我们也回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人你生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你担心真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受了伤不能隐瞒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟我这么见外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是一家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  脚很痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我变得孤零零的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都对我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而没有一个人斥责过我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  行人你说我们是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我背你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃又小又轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然大家都说小铃很坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃一直都是尽力地在勉强着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是既怕孤独又胆小
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.51,0:20:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
